ould organ variou social forc to take effect measur to protect and improv the live environ for aquat wildlif and also to protect and increas the propag of aquat wildlif resourc all unit and individu ar forbidden to damag the water habitat and live condit of aquat wildlif under nation and local major protect articl 8 all unit and individu have the right to report to local fisheri administr or their affili administr and supervis agenc act of seiz or damag aquat wildlif resourc and to accus the wrongdoer articl 9 ani unit or individu that discov aquat wild anim which ar wound or strand or which ar trap in inlet or river branch should report in a time manner to the local fisheri administr or it affili administr and supervis agenc so that thei can take emerg measur to rescu the anim thei can also request nearbi unit with the requisit resourc for rescu to take emerg measur and report to the fisheri administr at the same time dead aquat wild anim ar to be handl appropri by the fisheri administr aquat wild anim caught by mistak dure fish oper should be releas uncondition articl 10 applic can be made to the fisheri administr of the local peopl s govern for compens for damag caus by protect aquat wildlif under nation and local major protect the local govern will provid compens in accord with the relev provis of the provinci region or municip peopl s govern when the damag is prove to be true and merit compens after investig articl 11 the fisheri administr of the state council and of the peopl s govern of provinc autonom region and municip directli under the central govern should design natur reserv for aquat wildlif in the major habitat and water of aquat wildlif under nation and local major protect and propag and strengthen protect manag specif measur will be provid by the state council separ chapter 3 administr of aquat wildlif articl 12 catch and kill aquat wildlif under nation major protect is forbidden it is necessari to appli for a special permit for catch aquat wildlif under nation major protect when on of the follow situat occur 1 catch is necessari for scientif investig of aquat wildlif and aquat wildlif resourc 2 it is necessari to obtain individu of speci from natur water or habitat for tame and propag aquat wildlif under nation major protect 3 it is necessari to obtain aquat wildlif under nation major protect from natur water or habitat to undertak scientif research project abov provinci level or medic product task assign by the state 4 it is necessari to obtain aquat wildlif under nation major protect from natur water or habitat for propag and popular of knowledg about aquat wildlif teach or exhibit 5 it is necessari to obtain aquat wildlif under nation major protect due to other special circumst articl 13 procedur for applic for special catch permit 1 anyon who need to catch aquat wildlif under first class nation major protect should appli to the fisheri administr of the state council for a special catch permit with the sign opinion of the fisheri administr of the peopl s govern of the provinc autonom region or municip directli under the central govern where the applic resid and where the catch site is locat 2 anyon who need to catch aquat wildlif under second class nation major protect in their own provinc autonom region or municip directli under the central govern should appli to the fisheri administr of the peopl s govern of the provinc autonom region or municip directli under the central govern with the sign opinion of the fisheri administr of the peopl s govern of the counti where the applic resid 3 anyon who need to catch aquat wildlif under second class nation protect outsid their own provinc autonom region or municip directli under the central govern should appli for a special catch permit to the fisheri administr of the peopl s govern of the provinc autonom region or municip directli under the central govern where the catch site is locat with the sign opinion of the fisheri administr of the peopl s govern of the pr