aquat wildlif under nation major protect or it product and the import and export of aquat wildlif which is restrict by the intern convent of which china is a member or it product it is necessari to appli to the fisheri administr of the peopl s govern of the provinc autonom region or municip directli under the central govern where the import or export unit is locat or the applic resid the fisheri administr will submit the applic to the fisheri administr of the state council for approv after verif import and export busi activ should be undertaken by unit that have the right to import and export the commod concern import and export of the abov mention aquat wildlif by zoolog garden for exchang should be verifi and approv by the construct administr of the state council befor it is approv by the fisheri administr of the state council articl 24 econom return gain by hold exhibit of aquat wildlif or it product should mainli be us in the protect of aquat wildlif chapter 4 award and penalti articl 25 unit and individu that have perform on of the follow deed will be award by the peopl s govern abov counti level or it fisheri administr 1 outstand contribut to resourc investig protect and manag propag and educ and exploit and util of aquat wildlif 2 strict implement of the law for protect of wildlif with remark achiev 3 remark result in salvag protect tame and propag of aquat wildlif 4 great servic in prevent or report in a time manner the discoveri of act violat the law and regul for protect of aquat wildlif 5 great contribut in the investig of case in which wildlif resourc have been damag 6 great achiev in scientif studi of aquat wildlif or remark benefit attain in the applic and popular of relev research result 7 engag in the protect and administr of aquat wildlif in grass root unit for five year or more with remark result 8 other special contribut to the protect and administr of aquat wildlif articl 26 those who catch or kill aquat wildlif under nation major protect should 